  "description": "Resolve Missing Translation Keys in Program Sidebar Component\n\nIdentify and fix all missing translation keys in the .program-sidebar component to ensure all text displays properly in the application's supported languages.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate the .program-sidebar component file(s) in the codebase\n- Identify all instances where translation keys are missing or undefined\n- Add the missing translation keys to the appropriate locale/translation files\n- Provide translations for all supported languages in the application\n- Verify that all text in the sidebar renders correctly without fallback to key strings\n- Test the sidebar in different language settings to confirm translations display properly\n- Check for any hardcoded strings that should be using translation keys instead",
